social_posts.post_text: Dancehall Queen - Notting Hill Carnival 2022 💫

Lucky Gomez for your timeline 💘🍀
My son, my moon, my stars and everything in between …. Sucks when he can’t travel with me 😿
Always New York but I’m in London Town now ….. went to the Brit awards … memories were made and my sister @jodiesmith shut it downnnn of course 👑 … will post more later 💋

From JAMAICA with LOVE 🇯🇲 … so happy to finally get to share the beautiful shoot we did in JA 
Thank you @ebonymagazine for celebrating this beautiful moment!  Photography by the one and only @dapperlou !!!! Jodie is wearing all @shop_gonza 
The vibes were magical and effortless.  Lou came to hang with the fam while we floated, danced and laughed.  I styled the shoot with all GONZA pieces, shot the video, carried the speaker around, and held Lou’s equipment… while balancing a drink and dutty wining (of course). I can multitask 😹. Nothing makes me happier than creating art with my sister and talented creatives like Lou.  Thank you JAMAICA, me love youuuu 🇯🇲❤️‍🔥
Check out full story and the feature on @shop_gonza on @ebonymagazine .com
